\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The timer brought a smile to his face, his conversation so far hadn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t been as long as he thought. That gave him time to experiment a little. As he moved to sit down, he was immediately reminded of something he had almost forgotten. He was still stark naked. \u8220\'93Uh, I don\u8217\'92t suppose you could provide me with clothes by any chance? While I had kinda gotten distracted by everything else, I don\u8217\'92t normally run around in the nude\u8230\'85\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus could swear the Guide smirked at him as she waved her hand the way she had when conjuring his bedroll. A small bundle of what looked surprisingly like tan linen cloth appeared at his feet. Bending to examine it closer, it turned out to be a pair of linen drawstring pants, a loose, half-sleeved linen tunic, a pair of boxers made of what looked and felt like raw silk, and a pair of thin sandals that looked like they were made of leather.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He quickly started dressing himself, only for a thought to occur to him. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You could have done that at any time, couldn\u8217\'92t you?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yes.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 There was that little smirk again, he was sure of it this time. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So you just let me stay naked?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Essentially yes.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Why?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You didn\u8217\'92t ask for clothes sooner,\u8221\'94 she replied deadpan.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He closed his eyes and winced inwardly. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So I\u8217\'92ve been naked this whole time because I was too dumb to ask for clothes?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Essentially yes.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Grumbling to himself, Marcus finished dressing and sat cross-legged on the floor. The clothes were surprisingly comfortable and did little to impede movement. He spent another few long minutes considering everything he\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92d seen and learned so far. The System wasn\u8217\'92t overtly antagonistic but it didn\u8217\'92t appear to go out of its way to be helpful either. It answered relevant questions when asked, but didn\u8217\'92t start those conversations or suggest topics directly. It would provide things like bedding and clothes, but only in response to specific input from him\u8230\'85 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Are there any other techniques you can teach me before the next evaluation?\u8221\'94 It was certainly worth a shot at any rate. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The Guide paused again and this time he was almost positive she was querying the System. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Since you performed exceptionally in the first evaluation and have requested it, I can reward you by teaching you a meditation technique.\u8221\'94}}